<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw Nang kumsawt Suongpi muon um,
 Lalpa deihum ka hun muong;
 Lam tawnin kei ei veng inla,
 Na mel kipahum mu'ng ka.

[V2]
 Ei selin Aw kumsawt Suongpi,
 Na mel kipahum mudi'n;
 Damsung huiphpi ka thuok tieng leh,
 Kumsawt Suongpi ei selin.

[V3]
 2. Meipi hung zin tieng ei selin,
 Nisa hung vakkit masieh;
 Ka sep ka zawh ma'n ei vengin,
 Khawvel ka taihsan masieh.

[V4]
 3. Ka khuolzinna ka zawh tieng leh,
 Ka thagau chau nang puiin;
 Hukdampa mel ka muh masieh,
 Zie kumsawt gammnuom achun.</lyrics>
<title>ROCK OF AGES</title>
</song>